{"title":"老爷爷的话","authors":["祝智财"],"dates":[{"year":1958,"month":7,"day":15}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"老爷爷的话"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黑龙江拜泉县中起社农民  祝智财"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新社会，真正好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"想不到的都看到了："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有线广播墙上挂，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"社里已经有电话，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"县里召开广播会，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"坐在家里全记下。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"有位爷爷说的好，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个匣子真是宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"刮风下雨它先知道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国家的大事每天报，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"会唱歌，能奏乐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"相声、快板说的妙。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都说有神又有宝，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这下我可不信了，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"劳动人民就是神，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"科学东西都是宝。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}